data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
This program will guide you through the process of creating a SUI (Seven Update Information) file. Before you begin please read the documentation, you can view it by pressing F1.
Before you release your sui file to the public, it is a good idea to test it using the SUI validator on a test machine, this will ensure there are no problems.
